An AI-powered Resume and Interview Coach helps users craft impactful, ATS-friendly resumes by improving structure, optimizing bullet points, and tailoring content to specific job roles. It suggests stronger action verbs, quantifies achievements, and ensures clarity and relevance.

Beyond resumes, the tool conducts realistic mock interviews using role-specific questions and provides instant, personalized feedback on answers, communication, and confidence. By identifying gaps and offering actionable insights, it helps candidates continuously improve and perform better in real interviews.

Overall, it acts as a personalized career assistant, guiding users from resume building to interview success.
